# Project Folder Structure

## Core Directories
- **`src/`** - Source code (TypeScript modules, examples)
- **`tests/`** - Test files (Vitest TDD tests, Cucumber step definitions)
- **`features/`** - BDD feature files (Gherkin scenarios)
- **`dist/`** - Compiled JavaScript output
- **`docs/`** - Documentation and database files not accessible by llms
- **`reports/`** - Test reports and coverage data

## Configuration Files
- **Root level** - `package.json`, `tsconfig.json`, `eslint.config.js`, `vitest.config.ts`
- **`.cursor/`** - Cursor IDE rules, commands, and modes
- **`cucumber.config.cjs`** - Cucumber BDD configuration

## Key Files
- **`src/index.ts`** - Main entry point
- **`src/examples/`** - Example implementations
- **`tests/steps/`** - Cucumber step definitions
- **`features/*.feature`** - BDD scenarios in Gherkin syntax
- **`tests/*.test.ts`** - Vitest unit tests
